parameters:
Wow, what a great body! I'm jealous! Maybe I
should take my clothes off too...

There's a small oasis called Tarirari Oasis in the
northern part of the desert. It seems that
occasionally a highly skilled blacksmith comes
there, but they're mostly not around.

Will I be attacked if I walk around naked? Or are
you doing it on purpose?

I want to try eating at the Alvaan Tei at least
once. They say the food is incredibly delicious
and it makes you stronger.
